name: MultiplyDigitsQuiz
0:
”Alexa, open multiply digits quiz”
”Alexa, open multiply digits quiz and start”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: multiply digits quiz
des: This skill is intended to quiz the user on the multiplication times tables. The user will be presented with 10 problems and then given a score at the end. The high score is then kept so that the user can launch the skill again in the future and hear what the best score they have ever achieved previously.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
